          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-white/10">
        {services.map((service) => (
          <div class="bg-[#1a3a2a] p-8 md:p-10 hover:bg-[#2a5040] transition-colors duration-300 group">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <span class="text-5xl font-black text-[#c9973a]/30 tracking-tighter leading-none group-hover:text-[#c9973a]/50 transition-colors">{service.number}</span>
              <div class="w-8 h-px bg-white/20 mt-4 group-hover:bg-[#c9973a]/50 transition-colors"></div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-[#f5f0e8] tracking-tight mb-3">{service.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-[#b8b2a4] leading-relaxed mb-5">{service.description}</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#8a8678] tracking-wide">{service.detail}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== HOW IT WORKS ===== -->
  <section class="bg-[#ece5d5] py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[340px_1fr] gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <div class="w-6 h-px bg-[#c9973a]"></div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#c9973a] uppercase">Process</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#1a3a2a] tracking-tight leading-tight text-balance mb-6">
            How it works
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[#3d3d38] leading-relaxed">
            From onboarding to published article in under two weeks. Here is exactly what happens after you sign on.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-[#1a3a2a]/10">
          {[
            {
              step: 'Week 1',
              title: 'Store audit and keyword research',
              body: 'We audit your existing Shopify blog, product catalog, and competitor content. We identify the 30-50 highest-value keywords your brand is not yet targeting and build a content calendar ordered by opportunity score.',
            },
            {
              step: 'Week 2',
              title: 'First articles in review',
              body: 'You receive your first batch of articles in a shared Google Doc. Each article includes a brief explaining the target keyword, search volume, and why this topic was prioritized. You review, request changes if needed, and approve.',
            },
            {
              step: 'Ongoing',
              title: 'Publish, track, and compound',
              body: 'Articles are published to your Shopify blog on a consistent schedule. We monitor rankings monthly and adjust the content calendar as we identify what is gaining traction. Content compounds - each new article strengthens the ones before it.',
            },
            {
              step: 'Monthly',
              title: 'Performance report',
              body: 'Every month you receive a report showing keyword movement, impressions gained, and traffic attributed to EkimSEO content. You see exactly what your investment is doing.',
            },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="py-8 grid grid-cols-[100px_1fr] gap-6 items-start group">
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-[#c9973a] uppercase pt-1">{item.step}</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#1a3a2a] tracking-tight mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-[#3d3d38] leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== PRICING ===== -->
  <section id="pricing" class="bg-[#f5f0e8] py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-[#1a3a2a]/10">
