      <p class="text-center text-sm text-[#8a8678] mt-6">
        All plans are month-to-month. No contracts. <a href="mailto:mike@ekimseo.com" class="text-[#1a3a2a] underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-[#c9973a] transition-colors">Questions? Email mike@ekimseo.com</a>
